sive high-quality Chinese data** (far more emphasis than most Western models).\\n- Achieved **near-parity or even superiority to GPT-4-class models on Chinese tasks** while maintaining very strong English performance.\\n- This makes it one of the few model families that genuinely feels \"native\" in both Chinese and English.\\n\\n### 2. **The \"Everything Open\" Philosophy (2023\u20132025)**\\nAlibaba took a radically different approach from most Chinese labs:\\n\\n| Period       | Strategy                  | Impact |\\n|--------------|---------------------------|--------|\\n| 2023         | Open weights (7B, 14B)    | Huge |\\n| 2024         | Open **all** sizes (0.5B \u2192 **72B**) + MoE (235B) | Revolutionary |\\n| 2025         | Open **Qwen2.5-Omni** (multimodal) + **Qwen2.5-Coder** | Continued leadership |\\n\\nThis \"open by default\" stance became the defining characteristic of the Qwen family.\\n\\n### 3. **Technical Essence: Balanced Scaling + Data Quality**\\nThe real secret sauce of Qwen isn\\'t any single architectural trick, but rather:\\n\\n- **Extremely high-quality and diverse pre-training data** (especially Chinese web, books, code, math, and dialogue)\\n- **Very strong post-training** (SFT + RL) \u2014 Qwen2.5 models are particularly well-aligned\\n- **Excellent long-context handling** (up to 128K\u20131M in later versions)\\n- **Outstanding coding and mathematical reasoning** (especially Qwen2.5-Coder and Qwen2.5-Math)\\n\\n### 4. **The \"Qwen Spirit\"**\\nIf you had to distill the soul of the Qwen family into one sentence:\\n\\n> **\"Make the best possible models, make them as open as possible, and make them maximally useful to humanity \u2014 with China as the foundation.\"**\\n\\nThis is why Qwen went from \"just another Chinese model\" in 2023 to **one of the most respected and widely used model families in the world by 2025**, competing directly with Llama, DeepSeek, and even frontier closed models.\\n\\n**In short**:  \\n**Qwen = Chinese ro